      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of her, she\u2019s honestly in showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new car smell! I'm so sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 44500.0,
