    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This is an exceptional example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a mechanical limited-slip rear differential. Mechanically, this vehicle is flawless: the rod bearings have been preemptively addressed, the valve clearances are within factory spec, and the cooling system has been refreshed with an upgraded water pump. The chassis remains rigid, with a documented inspection of the rear subframe mounting points showing zero stress fractures. Every suspension component, from the control arm bushings to the dampers, maintains original damping rates and kinematics. This is a turn-key machine with a pristine underbody and a completely stock powertrain configuration, preserving the intended steering feedback and throttle response of this legendary platform.",
      "price": 44500.0,
